=Description=

"Fair Crowd Work collects information about crowd work, app-based work, and other "platform-based work" from the perspective of workers and unions. Uniquely, the site offers ratings of working conditions on different online labor platforms based on surveys with workers.

It is a joint project of IG Metall (the German Metalworkers' Union), the Austrian Chamber of Labor, the Austrian Trade Union Confederation, and the Swedish white collar union Unionen, in association with research and development partners Encountering Tech and M&L Communication Marketing."


